HEADWORD: Cobra de capello
<hw>Co"bra de ca*pel"lo</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Pg., serpent of the
hood.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The hooded snake (<spn>Naia
tripudians</spn>), a highly venomous serpent inhabiting India.<-- now
<gen>Naja</gen> --></def>⟦br⟧
